plot: As Marley battles the Mid-East Alliance to end a four-year war, a group of Warrior candidates on the front lines compete to be the successor of the Armored Titan.

Shifting focus to Marley's side after the truth of the Titan has been revealed. The Warriors and Eldian soldiers of Marley face the final clash against the Alliance Forces of the Mid-East, in the four-years international war at the battlefield of Fort Slava.—Anonymous

As a four year war between mid east federation and Marley draws to a close Four young Eldian soldiers in an 800 person unit fight against the enemy and each other for the place of the successor of the armoured titan. As Gabi comes up with a plan that lays it all on the line Zeke and Reiner have a surprise of their own waiting.

How long has it passed since the fierce battle between humans and giants began? On the other side of the sea, which Eren Yeager aimed for, there was a never-ending war. Who are they and what are they fighting for? Now, a child soldier is ready to die and throws himself into the front line.
